2002-08-09  Ryan Nunn  <colourles@users.sourceforge.net>
	* audio/midi_drivers/fmopl_midi.*, audio/midi_drivers/fmopldrv.cc,
	  gumps/AudioOptions_gump.cc : Fixing compiling issues
